    "The first assessed the performance of each additional feature individually against the baseline model by training a model which included the baseline feature scope plus that feature.",
    "The second assessed the cumulative performance by adding the features one by one and retraining each time.",
    "The order in which features were added was determined by their novelty, with features for which we have used a different methodology added first, followed by features not previously included.",
    "Ten percentage of the training dataset was set aside as a holdout set to evaluate the feature selection experiment.",
    "Models were trained using the remainder of the training dataset with a 90:10 train validation split."
